---
// Why section - Brand Lineage: minimal, calm
---

<section id="why">
	<div class="why-bg-shape"></div>
	<div class="tech-background"></div>
	<div class="why-container">
		<div class="section-label">WHY GORIGAMI</div>
		<h2>Why we exist</h2>
		<p class="why-copy">
			Great software doesn't need huge teams. It needs <strong
				>small, talented groups</strong
			> with clear ownership. We fold creativity, engineering, and brand into tools
			that actually move your business.
		</p>
		<ul class="why-bullets">
			<li>
				<span class="bullet-icon icon-target"></span>
				<span>Small teams, big impact</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<span class="bullet-icon icon-craft"></span>
				<span>Craft over hype</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<span class="bullet-icon icon-partnership"></span>
				<span>Partnership > projects</span>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	#why {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 8rem 10%;
		background: var(--smoke);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	/* Decorative background shape */
	.why-bg-shape {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -20%;
		left: -10%;
		width: 50%;
		height: 80%;
		background: var(--lavender-mist);
		clip-path: polygon(0% 20%, 60% 0%, 100% 80%, 40% 100%);
		z-index: 0;
		opacity: 0.5;
	}

	/* Tech background image - floating on left */
	.tech-background {
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 10%;
		width: 40%;
		height: 80%;
		background-image: url("/img/TechThings.png");
		background-size: contain;
		background-repeat: no-repeat;
		background-position: left center;
		opacity: 0.15;
		z-index: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.why-container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.section-label {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--sandy-brown);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	#why h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: var(--midnight-violet);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.why-copy {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--mid-gray);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 400;
	}

	.why-copy strong {
		color: var(--midnight-violet);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.why-bullets {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		border-left: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}

	.why-bullets li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--midnight-violet);
		font-weight: 400;
	}

	/* Minimal CSS Icons */
	.bullet-icon {
		width: 1.5rem;
		height: 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		position: relative;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	/* Target icon - concentric circles */
	.icon-target::before {
		content: "";
		width: 1.2rem;
		height: 1.2rem;
		border: 2px solid var(--sandy-brown);
		border-radius: 50%;
		position: absolute;
	}

	.icon-target::after {
		content: "";
		width: 0.6rem;
		height: 0.6rem;
		background: var(--sandy-brown);
		border-radius: 50%;
		position: absolute;
	}

	/* Craft icon - sparkle/star */
	.icon-craft::before {
		content: "âœ¦";
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--sandy-brown);
		line-height: 1;
	}

	/* Partnership icon - handshake symbol */
	.icon-partnership::before {
		content: "";
		width: 1rem;
		height: 0.5rem;
		border: 2px solid var(--sandy-brown);
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		position: absolute;
		transform: rotate(-15deg);
	}

	.icon-partnership::after {
		content: "";
		width: 1rem;
		height: 0.5rem;
		border: 2px solid var(--sandy-brown);
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		position: absolute;
		transform: rotate(15deg);
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
		#why {
			padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
		}

		/* Reduce tech background on mobile */
		.tech-background {
			opacity: 0.08;
			width: 60%;
		}

		#why h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.why-copy {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		.why-bullets {
			padding-left: 1.5rem;
		}

		.why-bullets li {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
